This paper deals with machine learning algorithms and their training and evaluation, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The focus is on image recognition, which is a common application of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses biases in datasets, which is a topic of interest in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper mentions the potential for adversarial attacks, which is a topic in computer security (cs.CR).
